name: So close yet so far away #1
description:
Two frigate birds soar in the air at dusk. It's 2021, and they can fly in the same air, just not too close to each other.

Based on the painting "So close yet so far away" by American artist Don Wesley, this animation pauses at the moment of the original painting's composition.

Don Wesley creates animated NFTs as companion collectibles for his canvas paintings. You can learn more about his work at https://donwesley.com
